    "channel_id": "C002SHOWPR",
    "reactions": null,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Greenhouse sensor hit 89°F right in the middle of my morning patients. Had to just leave it and hope the exhaust fan kicked in. Craig's at work, nobody home.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1791720000.000100",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C002SHOWPR",
    "reactions": null,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "89 is way too hot for orchids isn't it? Did Craig end up checking remotely?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1791730000.000200",
    "user_id": "U003RACHEL"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C002SHOWPR",
    "reactions": null,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "He did. Exhaust vent was stuck — he opened it from the app and it dropped to 76 in about twenty minutes. Disaster narrowly averted.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1791808000.000300",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C002SHOWPR",
    "reactions": null,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Ok thank god. You would've been devastated. Also impressed Craig knows how to work the app lol",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1791894000.000400",
    "user_id": "U005DOROTHY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C002SHOWPR",
    "reactions": null,
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "He learned fast after the January freeze scare. Motivation. Those cattleyas are three of my six entries for the regional — losing them now would have been a catastrophe.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1791900000.000500",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
